Model

Class Photo

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.Photo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Photo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Photo is used to manipulate data associated with an individual photo It holds an array of tags, a name, a date, the source of the photo, and the current active photo, as well as other fields associated with photo
    Author:
    Tom Raybould & Mike Tomkowich
    See Also:
